data.description: Come see this charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage home conveniently located on a corner lot. Entertainment is a breeze with a screened lanai facing a pond view. You will love the savings on your electric bill since this home is fitted with solar panels. Primary bedroom has a beautiful end-suite that will accommodate everyone with his-and-her sinks and closets. You won't want to let this one pass you by!  Solar panels are included with the sale of the property paid in full by seller just installed less than a year ago. Garage door opener and Ring doorbell are all included. Also comes with ceiling fans in master bedroom, living room and 1 of the other bedrooms. Beautiful Gated Community that has only about 30 homes.
